Basic Selection: Retrieve the titles and release dates of all songs released in 2022, ordered by release date (newest first).

SELECT 
title, 
release_date
FROM Songs 
WHERE release_date >= '2022-01-01'
AND release_date < '2023-01-01'
ORDER BY release_date DESC;

Filtering: Find all songs with a popularity score greater than 80 and a duration less than 4 minutes (240 seconds).

SELECT
title,
popularity_score,
duration_seconds
FROM Songs
WHERE popularity_score > 80
AND duration_seconds < 240;

Pattern Matching: List all artists whose names start with "The".

SELECT 
artist_name 
FROM Artists 
WHERE artist_name LIKE 'The%';

Multiple Conditions: Find all premium customers who joined in 2022.

SELECT 
customer_id,
premium_member,
join_date
FROM Customers
WHERE join_date LIKE '2022%';

Calculations and Aliasing: Calculate the total duration (in minutes) of all songs in the database and display the result with an appropriate column name.

SELECT
    ROUND(SUM(duration_seconds) / 60.0, 2) AS total_duration_minutes
FROM songs;

Advanced Filtering: Find the top 5 most expensive song purchases in the database.

SELECT
purchase_id,
song_id,
price
FROM Purchases
ORDER BY price DESC 
LIMIT 5;


Using Multiple Tables Separately: First, find all song_ids from songs with a popularity score above 90. Then, use those song_ids to find purchases of those songs.

SELECT 
song_id
FROM Songs
WHERE popularity_score > 90;

SELECT 
purchase_id,
song_id,
purchase_date,
price
FROM Purchases
WHERE song_id IN (SELECT 
song_id
FROM Songs
WHERE popularity_score > 90);


Range Checking: Find all purchases made between January 1, 2023 and March 31, 2023.

SELECT 
song_id,
purchase_id,
purchase_date,
price
FROM Purchases
WHERE purchase_date BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-03-31';


Advanced Filtering with ORDER BY: Identify the songs with the highest popularity scores (above 90).

SELECT 
song_id,
title,
popularity_score
FROM Songs
WHERE popularity_score > 90
ORDER BY popularity_score DESC;